{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemechipcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of chip","type":"text"}]},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"chip","type":"text"}]},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSChip","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllChipComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"ChipComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Chip","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"colors (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") , spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and border  (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for chip component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomChipComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the chip component tokens you want.","","        override var chipSizeMaxHeight: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.dimension500 }","","        override var chipBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.borderWidthmediumt }","","        override var chipColorBgFocus: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.colorContentDefault }","","        override var chipSpaceInsetIconOnly: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.spacePaddingInlineTall }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomChipComponentTokensProvider: ChipComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomChipComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(chip: CustomChipComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(chip: CustomChipComponentTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let chipComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, border, color and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let chipComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.10.0","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Since","style":"note"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDS